text.tspan: Prevalence of eating disorders by age, World, 1990 to 2017
Share of population within each age category with the eating disorders anorexia or bulimia nervosa. This is
measured across both sexes. Figures attempt to provide a true estimate (going beyond reported diagnosis) of
eating disorder prevalence based on medical, epidemiological data, surveys and meta-regression modelling.
Source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease
